entries.definition:
w–j–h face, front, facade; direction, point of view, variety;
main point; correct method; person of distinction, honour; to face;
to turn towards, to make for, to direct, to turn something towards.
Of this root, six forms occur 78 times in the Qur’an: وَجَّهَ wajjaha
twice; تَوَجَّهَ tawajjaha once; وَجْه wajh 34 times; وُجُوه wujūh 38

